Description:
    This generator adds Decision Records and Architecture Decision Records (ADR) to your project

Example:
    bin/rails generate hdi:ways_of_working:decision_record

    This will create:
        architecture-decision-record/README.md
        architecture-decision-record/ADRXXX-architecture-decision-record-template.md
        architecture-decision-record/ADR000-record-architecture-decisions.md
        decision-record/README.md
        decision-record/DRXXX-decision-record-template.md
        decision-record/DR000-use-github-and-the-adr-process.md
